QuestData.Title: Lost Sheepie
QuestData.Description: Chee Chee's prize sheep, Sheepie, is missing!$B$BThat bad sheep is always wandering off the farm.$B$BStupid sheep! I looked everywhere and couldn't find him.$B$BCan you help me, $r?
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Sheepie and return him to Chee Chee.
